Current high-precision survey-in mean positionECEF X coordinate. Must be in the range -99..+99.The current survey-in mean position ECEF Xcoordinate, in units of cm, is given bymeanX + (0.01 * meanXHP)

Current high-precision survey-in mean positionECEF Y coordinate. Must be in the range -99..+99.The current survey-in mean position ECEF Ycoordinate, in units of cm, is given bymeanY + (0.01 * meanYHP)

Current high-precision survey-in mean positionECEF Z coordinate. Must be in the range -99..+99.The current survey-in mean position ECEF Zcoordinate, in units of cm, is given bymeanZ + (0.01 * meanZHP)
